title: Adventures of Superman v2 1-9 (2013) (digital) (Minutemen-PhD)
description:
English | CBR | 9 Issues

Adventures of Superman v2 #1-9
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  April 29, 2013 - June 24, 2013

Writers:  Jeff Parker (#1), Jeff Lemire (#2), Justin Jordan (#3), J.M. DeMatteis (#4), Joshua Hale Fialkhov (#5), Bryan J.L. Glass (#6), Michael Avon Oeming (#6), and Matt Kindt (#7-9)
Artists:  Chris Samnee (#1), Jeff Lemire (#2), Riley Rossmo (#3), Giuseppe Camuncoli (#4), Sal Buscema (#4), Joelle Jones (#5), Michael Avon Oeming (#6), and Stephen Segovia (#7-9)
Colorists:  Matthew Wilson (#1), Jose Villarrubia (#2), Riley Rossmo (#3), Tony Avina (#4), Nick Filardi (#5-6), and Jay David Ramos (#7-9)
Letterer:  Wes Abbott

Join comics' finest talents as they celebrate the Man of Steel himself--Superman! This digital-first anthology features the Last Son of Krypton in timeless tales of truth and justice. Up, up, and away!

Thanks goes to PhD for this release.
